			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Playing a medium to high level wizzy?  I have two words for you: Gallenite Bracelet.  There is a lot of animosity in this Wizzy thread against Mages.  They are your friend.  They can create Gallenite Bracelets which substantially increase damage of nukes.  The spell Summon Jade Bracelet is a level 20 mage spell, and I typically tip 5pp for it's casting (the spell itself only costs 6pp, so this is rather generous, but the effect is amazing).  The spell is a Lucelin spell, found upstairs at the bazaar. If you can, find a level 51 Mage for the Ruby bracelet or a level 61 for the saphire bracelet.  The level 44 Opal bracelet has a chaos effect I don't like, and I prefer the Jade.  I am a circle 38 wizzy and I gained my past two levels soloing in Feerrott with these bracelets.  I buy them from Mages at the Nexus or Planes of Power.  These bracelets are NO RENT.  You can wear two at a time, but the damage multiplier doesn't double up - only the bonus to AC and Mana.
				</font>
			</td>

