	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Hello wizards!  <BR>
Got to say, I have been enjoying playing the wizard. Made 34 recently and Im enjoying new spells very much. (Especially Harvest!)  Got my Staff of Temperal Flux. (YOU MUST DO THIS QUEST!) I saw in a previous post someone asked what equipment he should get. Well, I thought I'd share what I have. Note: most of the this stuff is fairly cheap if you have a main that's about 40+ that can get the money for you. I spent about 1k total on most my gear. <BR>
<BR>
Advisor's Robe: Awesome Robe can get for 500PP<BR>
Black Chiten legs: 100pp<BR>
(2) Moonstone rings: 50pp pair<BR>
Strawspun belt: 20pp (10AC nice for casters!)<BR>
Runed Circlet: 100pp<BR>
Frog Skin Mask: 50pp (DE only)<BR>
(2) Polished Bone Bracers: 100pp for pair<BR>
(2) Gold Stud earrings: 60pp for pair<BR>
<BR>
The rest is woven armor that I've looted off of Frogloks in Guk. (Same AC as Raw Silk Armor but fits ALL sizes)<BR>
I also won some Azure sleeves (AC12 WOOT!) from killing the Mino Patriark in Live side LGuk. (easy camp by the zone)<BR>
<BR>
This gear carried me well up to 30+.  And Im always on the look out for new gear. <BR>
<BR>
Now, you say &quot;Oh sure!  You got a main to hand money down to ya!&quot;  Actually, when you become Port capable, you'll have people throwing money at you. Money will be no issue. However, remember when you're porting making money, you're not gaining exps. Kind of a trade off. Be sure to balance out the two so you can fully develope your character. <BR>
<BR>
One more suggestion: Train all you can into RESEARCH!  Most research spells are Area of Effect spells. If you dont have AoE spells, you cant quad-kite! Even if you already have the spell scribed, you should still research the spells your runes make. And spend Training points\money at every level past 16. You dont want to fail when it's time to make that Ice Comet spell do you?  (1120 DD!) Auction your extra spells and feel free to trade runes with other Wizards. I've met quite a few wizards and I've found we all get along pretty well!  There is a bond between wizards and we should help each other out as much as we can. You'd be suprised how much you'll bennefit from helping others!<BR>
<BR>
Well that was a very long post, however I want to help with the success of our class and not initiate hostility towards others. YOU GAIN NOTHING FROM THAT!<BR>
<BR>
Good luck everyone!<BR>
<BR>
Starleen of Orion's Honor<BR>
34 Wizard<BR>
Brell Serelis Server
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
</table><br>
